quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  88,1,"Has the news of the overwhelming event reached you?",footnotes:182690:1
  88,2,"Some faces that Day shall be downcast with fear,",footnotes:182691:1
  88,3,"be toiling and worn-out;"
  88,4,"they shall burn in a Scorching Fire;"
  88,5,"their drink shall be from a boiling spring."
  88,6,"They shall have no food except bitter dry thorns",footnotes:182692:1
  88,7,"that will neither nourish nor satisfy their hunger."
  88,8,"On that very Day some faces shall be radiant with joy,"
  88,9,"well-pleased with their striving.",footnotes:182693:1
  88,10,"They will be in a lofty Garden"